translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_994afe76:
    # "Sarah drafted her orders and handed them down."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_eaa69cc9:
    # "From her hands, to her commanders, to the officers and soon down to every last man and woman in her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_72c1c4fa:
    # "The warcamp swelled with excitement. The eagerness of soldiers too long denied a battle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_66a55ece:
    # "Perhaps only the old knew of the carnage to come, but few soldiers lived to be old."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_ffb98eb5:
    # "By early next morning, the army had completed its preparations and begun to march."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_090a9d90:
    # "Riding near the lead, Sarah surveyed her army, trying to coax out any weakness she had perhaps missed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_3cf53a05:
    # "The snow slowed them down, but not by as much as she had feared."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_81879fbb:
    # "Many of the soldiers in her army were Rosannan natives, familiar with the hard winters."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e59e06d7:
    # "As they marched, they soon found themselves coming upon the crossroad."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_fd55bbf6:
    # "This was where the main road split off into the Hinterlands, the far-removed backwater provinces of Rosanna."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_7b3ab417:
    # "Watching the dire condition of the road, Sarah wondered if she had not made a mistake."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_51600b3b:
    # "Regardless, it was too late to stop now."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_dfc25a98:
    # "Her army headed off towards the Hinterlands, leaving the main road behind."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_d5d0edb1:
    # "At first, the soldiers continued to march on the road that led into the Hinterlands."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_b48b1bc2:
    # "But soon, the quality of the road declined so much, that their metal boots cracked the earth and turned it to mud."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_67fbb624:
    # "The wagons, carrying the army supplies found their wheels caught in the deep mud, slowing the march."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_2172ccde:
    # "As some wagons sank into the mud, others became stuck behind them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_27a9e228:
    # "The soldiers were instructed to march besides the road, leaving the road proper only for the wagons."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c134e1bb:
    # "It improved their situation, but only by so much."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_dc968f2f:
    # "The soldiers themselves, now forced to march through the fields, thick with snow, struggled."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_5df157fe:
    # "Cold winds assaulted them for every mile they crossed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_db639cb5:
    # "And as far as the horizon, nothing but vast fields of blinding white snow."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c68a8c43:
    # "Two days in these miserable conditions."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_dd0b9458:
    # "Two days of suffering the elements, before her army came upon the nearest place that could be called a town."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_49b08fff:
    # "A brief respite. A chance to restock."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_3a274ad3:
    # "Her army marched into the town, stunned and confused peasants looking on."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_d75dfa19:
    # "Sarah made her way into the town's tavern."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_b1a4dee0:
    # "Most of her soldiers would have to make camp outside of the town. The lucky few could find a hovel to rent for the night."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_23bf0ba1:
    # "Sarah sat down in the tavern."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_da95615f:
    # "Around her, commanders swarming, planning, advising."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c73a1ff7:
    # "Their plans, only days old, had already been delayed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e34a8fd4:
    # "The roads were worse than she had feared. The elements harsher."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_17e2c8e5:
    # "A nervous innkeeper came up to her table and served her some beer and food."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_b5d5ba8a:
    # s "Thank you."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_4c893662:
    # "Innkeeper" "No...it's nothing, really...my honor to serve..."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_84688cbf:
    # "His voice trembled."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_430077ce:
    # "Sarah looked at him, confused."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_653ef73f:
    # s "What is it?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_886d026b:
    # "Innkeeper" "Nothing, nothing. Forgive me, your Grace."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_cb0c66df:
    # "The man stumbled away."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_3744586a:
    # "Sarah followed him with her eyes, unsure of what to make of the strange innkeeper."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e7d9a006:
    # "Sitting around the table, Sarah held court as an endless stream of commanders and officers pleaded for her attention."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_50496feb:
    # "For every issue she solved, two others would be dropped in her lap."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_85b49ed7:
    # "Sarah looked over and saw Samayra, argueing with a few officers, telling them stay away."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_4a6e78d1:
    # "Sarah smiled, happy that she at least had Samayra, a capable secretary that could keep her schedule manageable."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_02b2580e:
    # "It was late into the night when a group of about four men stumbled into the tavern."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_34ef6db1:
    # "Sarah frowned as she watched them stumble inside, shouting loudly."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_7c199517:
    # "Man" "Hail Sarah Rose!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_f51900e5:
    # "Second man" "She'll show those Savages!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_91edb975:
    # "The men stumbled further into the room, the guards held them at a distance."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_1c41085f:
    # "Man" "Hey! No need to fight us, we're just here to celebrate her Highness!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c63b99ea:
    # "The man raised a flask filled with something that reeked of strong alcohol."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e80294e5:
    # "Sarah slightly nodded, acknowledging the man without hoping to encourage him."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_20f2668f:
    # "Second man" "Ay! Cheers to that!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_49edf96e:
    # "Second man" "Finally someone that's gonna return the King's Law to these lands!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e119bdbe:
    # "Second man" "Or the Queen's Law, my lady, apologies!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c3e57b97:
    # "He raised his drink along with this friends."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_3e66da9d:
    # "Man" "Speaking of justice and law! I would wish to pe...pet...peti..."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_82a55279:
    # "Second man" "Petition."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_6f8f27c7:
    # "Man" "Petition! I would like to petition the Court!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_72370eca:
    # "Sarah sighed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_4aa90e66:
    # "It had been a long tradition that the people of Rosanna were permitted to offer up their grievances to their king or queen."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_1cec5b1d:
    # "In the past, they would have had to submit a written request, have it signed by a local lord, and then it would make its way into the bureaucracy of the state."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_9bc2bf1a:
    # "From local lord, to provincal lord, to the court's secretary, and on and on."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_9589e88c:
    # "It was a long and tiring process, mostly designed to filter out the endless trivial requests that people would submit."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_062fe50d:
    # "But Sarah had only her army, and so instead, she suffered a request that by tradition, she was bound to hear."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c2b82b7f:
    # s "Fine, offer up your petition, but make it quick."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_ab529ef5:
    # "The man stumbled forward, clearly already inebriated."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e53eba02:
    # "He cleared his throat, doing his best to sound presentable."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_8ad7003a:
    # "Man" "Your Grace...your Highness...I..."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_f3474d54:
    # "Sarah gestured with her hands for him to move it along."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_683cabef:
    # s "Just say it."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_dd8bf87f:
    # "Man" "We in this town have been faithful loyalists to your family."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_9a69a308:
    # "Man" "And for it, we have paid dearly."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_d847460a:
    # "Man" "Our town is to small to be permanently occupied, so each month, an emmissary from the Tribes rides out and hands out punishments."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_f751da48:
    # "Man" "Those who keep their heads down, are left alone."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_2a424d5b:
    # "Man" "Those who are loyal, are punished."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e99319ff:
    # "He paused for a short while."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_b1f8b86f:
    # "Man" "And those who conspire with your enemies, who colaborate with the Tribes, they are rewarded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_a4c9c197:
    # "Man" "They spy on their neighbours. Rat out loyalists. Condemn them and their families to suffer at the hand of the Tribes."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_80dc2d04:
    # "Man" "And for it, the Tribes reward them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_40aa162e:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_28027326:
    # "She wasn't too surprised to learn of this. The Tribes had little interest in direct rule, they simply wanted to keep the populace down."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_5c54f3db:
    # "This was an effective, not very costly, way of doing it."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_0046b5e6:
    # s "I understand what you're saying, but what is your petition?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_5e8363b4:
    # "The man gestured towards the far end of the tavern."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_8e773544:
    # "Sarah saw the innkeeper, shaking. His face, pale."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_2d787f2c:
    # "Man" "That man...that man that served you your drink, and your food, he used to be little more than a farmhand and a thief."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_27bc0903:
    # "Man" "No more than a few years ago, he travelled from town to town, begging for work, and stealing what he couldn't earn honestly."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_dba57843:
    # "Man" "A vagrant."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_a540d3d4:
    # "Man" "Now, he looks all prim and proper, owner of this here tavern."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_2c725762:
    # "Man" "But what he probably forgot to mention was that this tavern used to have a previous owner."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_a55d8bad:
    # "Man" "A proper and rightious man, that held loyal to you and your family."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_92849d03:
    # "Man" "And for that loyalty, the Tribesmen gave him the rope. They gave him the rope because this creature ratted him out."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_40035894:
    # "Man" "And they gave him the tavern as a reward."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_c6d592cc:
    # "The man stepped forward, anger growing on his face."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_31c1ce12:
    # "On the far end of the room, Sarah saw the innkeeper, his entire body now shaking."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_ae35424a:
    # "A young woman had come out from the kitchen and stood next to him, a confused yet frightened expression on her face as well."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_4fef80a9:
    # "Man" "You have come to our town. Liberated us from the yoke of the Tribesmen."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_a9c3d9d3:
    # "Man" "I ask you...petition you...what kind of a country will you build?"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_28448b24:
    # "Man" "Is it one where vermin like him live large? Or will you build a country as your Father did."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_2d515a0b:
    # "Man" "One where justice rules, and men like him get what they deserve?"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_133ea603:
    # "The room went silent."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_0274058c:
    # "Sarah saw everyone's eyes on her. A heavy silence growing deeper by the second."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_47190df5:
    # "The man and his friends were clearly drunk."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_1dfa3d08:
    # "Whatever justice they had in mind was likely not going to involve a judge."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_b6244887:
    # "Yet, if their story was true, then the innkeeper was a turncoat. A traitor that turned on her family the moment they fell out of power."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_33d6e66b:
    # "What use did she have for subjects that would betray her the moment her rule weakened?"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_47be1e5d:
    # "And wasn't it right that a man who earned his fortune through treason, stood to lose it?"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_239fec51:
    # "Sarah saw the innkeeper, clutching the young woman, holding her close."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_63248e48:
    # "Not his wife, she reasoned. His daughter."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_16cf1372:
    # "Sarah paused for a moment longer, considering the case."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_e293cab0:
    # "The innkeeper might well deserve whatever came to him...but this was a mob. A mob asking for her approval."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Hinterlands_5c37820c:
    # "And the mob would likely not spare the girl their wrath."
    ""

